quran[59]{c,v,t}:
  26,52,"Nabii Muusal:yi-naqoosak yeemene mara barat kuulus iyyaanamah wacyi kaal oobisne, diggah firqawnaa kee kay qande sin kataatele sin gacsaanamkeh axcuk"
  26,53,Tokkel firqawni kay reedah gubaak tan magaaloolih qaskar ruube macaxu kaah kobxisaanamkeh israa-iil xaylok mawuq yoobbe waqdi
  26,54,"Firqawni: diggah a-mari (israa-iil xaylo kinnuk) dago horta iyye"
  26,55,Kaadu diggah usun kaxxam nee ceerissa taama aben
  26,56,"Diggah nanu inkih cibbarsimaah, gulguluh keenih yan mara kinnino iyye"
  26,57,Firqawnaa kee kay mara Masri baaxoy basaatin kee daroori-lek ken neyyeeqeh
  26,58,Kaadu kadnoonii kee meqe aroocaay meqe qarwak ken neyyeeqe
  26,59,"Too mayyuq keenit kah abne innah, kaadu ken dabooqaa kee ken maalu israa-iil xaylo nagarsisne ken bayisneek gamadal"
  26,60,Tokkel firqawnaa kee kay macaxi Nabii Muusaa kee kaâ luk yan mara ayro edde tawqe waktit kataaten
  26,61,"Tokkel namma butta (firqawni maraa kee Muusâ mara kinnuk) sitta tuble waqdi, Nabii Muusâ kataysis:diggah nanu elel simneeh firqwnaa kee kay macxi nee qide-le iyyen"
  26,62,"Nabii Muusa keenik iyyeh: aleey, sin meeleelan, diggah anu yoo qokla Rabbi liyooh, edde naggoowa gita yoh ascasse-le"
  26,63,"Tokkel Nabii Muusal isi caxxat bad atuk iyyaanamah wacyi kaal oobisne, tokkel usuk kaa yootokeeh, bad baxsimeeh kulli exxa kaak kaxxa qaleh innah gacca itte"
  26,64,Kaadu tokkel aka mara xayyosne (firqawnaa kee kay mara kinnuk) badat cullu iyyaanam fanah Muusaa kee Muusâ marih lakal
  26,65,Kaadu Nabii Muusaa kee kaâ luk yan mara inkih naggosneh
  26,66,Tohuk lakal aka mara badat xuumusne (firqawnaa kee kay macaxu kinnuk)
  26,67,"Diggah tohut Yallih inkittinaanee kee kay dudda tascasse astá tan, kaadu keenik maggo mari yeemene mara makkinna"
  26,68,"Kaadu diggah ku-Rabbi, usuk maysoli xuwawli kinni"
  26,69,Kaadu Nabiyow ama korosul Nabii Ibraahim xaagu maaqaay keenil akriy
  26,70,Usuk isi abbaa kee isi marak taqbudeenim maatiyaay iyye waqdi
  26,71,"Numtinwwellitte naqbudeeh, tet amol daffeyak asna tet qibaadah iyyen"
  26,72,"Nabii Ibraahim isin ken kallactan waqdi, usun sin yaabbeenih innaa? keenik iyye"
  26,73,"Hinnay ken tuqbudeenik tu siinih xiqaanaa, hinnay ken aqbude wayteenik tu siinik kalaanaa keenik iyye"
  26,74,"Aleey!wohuk tu maabaanay, ni- abbobti nanu abnah innah taama neh abak sugteeh nanu wohul ken salleeh ken katatne iyyen"
  26,75,"Nabii Ibraahim keenik iyyeh:yoh warisay numtinwwellittek aqbudak sugteenim cubbiluk wagitteenii iggimaa kee makot taniinim sinnik taaxagoonuh"
  26,76,Sin kee siinik naharsi abbobti
  26,77,"Diggah usun yok qaduwwiiy ken maqbuda, kinnih immay anu aqbudem ginô Rabbi kinni, usuk addunyaa kee akeeral yok awlaytu"
  26,78,Yallay tayse ginoh yoo gine usuk meqe gital tirri yoo hee-le
  26,79,"Kaadu Kaa kinni yoo taskameeh, yoo tafqem"
  26,80,Kaadu biyaakita waqdi biyaakak usuk yoo qaffoysa
  26,81,"Kaadu Kaa kinni yoo qiddaah, sarra yoo taynuwweem Qhiyaamah ayró"
  26,82,Kaadu Ķaa kinni yi-dambi yoh cabam kak qaagitam galtóh ayró (Qhiyaamah ayró kinnuk)
  26,83,"Nabii Ibraahim isi Rabbi kallacak:yi-Rabbow tu-xiqta ixxiga yoh acuyaay, ku naqoosak meqe mara yoo eleelis iyye"
  26,84,"Kaadu meqe saareey, meqe xagar xagó (galab-xagó) yoh ab ellecabô maray yok lakal yamaatu waah addal Qhiyaamah ayrô fanah"
  26,85,Kaadu ku-naqoosak naqiim deqsita Jannat nagra marat yoo hayis
  26,86,"Kaadu yi-abbah dambi cab, diggah usuk makkoote marak numuk teynah sugek"
  26,87,Kaadu yoo mawacarriysin ginó inkih magooqak cisab kee galtoh ugussa ayrò (Qhiyaamah ayro kinnuk)
  26,88,Woh gibdi ayróy maaluu kee xaylo tu edde xiqe wayta kinni
  26,89,"Yallâ fanah saytun lubbi luk yemeete num akke waytek, koroosannuu kee munaafiqhinnuk"
  26,90,"Kaadu Yallak meesiteeh, kay taaqatal kaâ fanah yufkune marah Jannat xayyoysimaah ken yaybulleenih Qhiyaamah ayrò"
  26,91,Kaadu jaciim deqsitta girá koroosite maray tirtô gitak makkoote yaybulleenih
  26,92,"Kaadu ken sahitak:sin yallittey aqbudak sugteeni annih teetiiy? Keenik iyyan"
  26,93,Yallak kalah aqbudak sugteenim Yallih digaalák sin cattaa hinnay is isi nafsi Yallih digaalák cattaa
  26,94,Tokkel ken (numtinwwellittee kee koros kinnuk) kee tirtô gitak makkoote mara xambabbaqqa ken heenih jahannamat foocah (neefih) qambisiman
  26,95,Kaadu ibliis qande (kaa kataate mara kinnuk) inkih teetit qambisimta
  26,96,Koros kee usun aqbudak sugeenim tet addal anuk keemaaritak ittak iyyaanah
  26,97,Yallal xiibitna immay nanu diggah addunyal baxxaqqa itta makoy qellu sinnih addat sugne itta koros
  26,98,Nanu Ginô Rabbit sin massosne waqdi Qibaadal
  26,99,Kaadu tirtô gitak nee makkossem matan umeyniitiy Yallak kalih im naqbudeemih neh secte akke waytek
  26,100,"A-saaku shafaaqatta neh takkeeh, Yallih digaalak nee cattaamak num mannu"
  26,101,Kaadu kacnoytah yan kataysay neh xuwaawa (allaaqala) mannu
  26,102,Maganey!inki adda addunyâ fanah madaara luk sugnaamal yeemene maray naggoowê loowot gacak nen iyyan
  26,103,"Diggah too Nabii Ibraahim xaaguy taturet kaskassoowa marah astá tan, kaadu keenik ama xaagu yoobbe marak maggom yeemene mara makko"
  26,104,Kaadu diggah Nabiyow ku-Rabbi usuk mayso-li xuwaw-li kinni
  26,105,"Nabii Nuuc mari sinni farmoyta Nuuc dirabboyseeh, wohul farmoytit inkih dirabboyse mara yekken"
  26,106,Ken toobokoyti Nabii Nuuc Yallak mameesittaanaa?keenik iyye waqdi
  26,107,Diggah anu siinih amaanat-le farmoyta kinniyo edde rubsumem sin gudduysaamal
  26,108,Toysa Yallak meesitaay yi-amri oggola
  26,109,"Kaadu Yallih farmo sin gudduysaamal galtó sin messera, yi-galtó numul matanaay numul messera ginô Rabbil essera yoo akke waytek"
  26,110,Toysa Yallak meesitaay yi-amri oggola